Ada Benjamin (amuru 18 Mee 1994) bu onye n'eme egwuregwu Naijiria, ọ bu ọpụrụiche n'ịgba sprinting
N'afọ 2014, na asọmpi Commonwealth na Glasgow ọ meriri nrite ọlaọcha na 4 × 400 m relay na Patience Okon George, Regina George na Folashade Abugan
Ọ na-agụ akwụkwọ na Mahadum Texas, El Paso (UTEP), ọ na-agụ izụ ahịa
Benjamin bụ onye otu egwu ime ime na n'èzí UTEP
